      • createUser

        public User createUser(String username,
                       String password)
                throws SQLException
        Saving a user to the database without isAdmin or balance specified. This method sets isAdmin to false and the balance to 0
        Parameters:
        username - Desired username
        password - Desired password (not enctrypted when stored in the database)
        Returns:
        The userobject of the user created
        Throws:
        SQLException - If the user already exists (double entry)

      • createUser

        public User createUser(String username,
                       String password,
                       boolean isAdmin,
                       double balance)
                throws SQLException
        Save a user to the database.
        Parameters:
        username - A unique username (primary key in database)
        password - Password for log in (not encrypted)
        isAdmin - the user type: true if the user isAdmin and false if it's a regular user.
        balance - the balance of the user.
        Returns:
        A userobject of the user created in the database.
        Throws:
        SQLException - If the user already exists (double entry)

        Parameters:

        Returns:
